long_description:
# Narutomaki!

The delicious narutomaki! Crafted from fish, flour and pink dye, depending on what mod you have.

Fish mods: [Ethereal NG](https://content.luanti.org/packages/TenPlus1/ethereal/), or [MineClone2 game](https://content.luanti.org/packages/Wuzzy/mineclone2/)

Flour mods: [Minetest Game](https://content.luanti.org/packages/Minetest/minetest_game/), [Farming Redo](https://content.luanti.org/packages/TenPlus1/farming/), or [MineClone2 game](https://content.luanti.org/packages/Wuzzy/mineclone2/)
